{"type": "article", "id": 2273, "title": "扶手旁边加口袋的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-10T00:58:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222316TkCR4ObLg67Npn0D.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t挪威设计团队 Angell,Wyller &amp; Aarseth 日前带来一款名为“ Saddle ”d的椅子，其特别指出在于为扶手两侧设置的大口袋，方便收纳杂志、书籍、遥控器等各类物品，取用方便。Saddle 是一款全手工制作完成的椅子，以橡木或白蜡木作为框架的主要材质，椅垫则提供软羊皮与羊毛毡两种材质，多色可选。定价 12900 挪威克朗，<a href=\"http://www.slaake.no/produkter/saddle\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222314XdRWmwkecSUZCG74.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222314Pw7ztSas4r5HG26Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222315fpZyD6eBJW8M3iQj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222315OWJG4vk2RlZ69VdS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}